summary: An ordinance relating to the Engineering Department, pertaining to the preparation of plans and specifications for the construction of traffic interchanges or grade separations and certain other work at 15th Avenue West and West Garfield Street, and certain other locations in accordance with provisions of Ordinance No. 83369; and amending Section 2 of Ordinance No. 84951 by increasing the appropriation authorized therein from the Seattle General Arterial Improvement Bonds 1954 Fund.
